Class NtpTimeConfigurationParam

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.colibris.nsd.NtpTimeConfigurationParam

  • public class NtpTimeConfigurationParam
extends java.lang.Object
    This NtpTimeConfigurationParam class provides parameters given by NTP (e.g. the time offset between the server and the client, the round trip delay, and a flag that determines if the clients is already synchronised with the server
